[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0308","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0696","title":"多厂商 CDE Calendar Manager Service Daemon (rpc.cmsd) 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CDE 日历管理服务守护进程（rpc.cmsd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenUnix 8.0/UnixWare 7.1.1、HP HP-UX 11.0、Solaris 7.0 及 SunOS 4.1.4 等多个 Unix 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0696"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.067","remediation":"建议立即安装各厂商对应安全补丁：Solaris 7.0 安装补丁 106827-01 或 106828-01，HP-UX 11.0 安装 PHSS_19757 补丁，UnixWare 7.1.1 安装 erg711905 补丁。如无法打补丁，可在 inetd.conf 中注释掉 rpc.cmsd 服务行并重启 inetd，或在防火墙层面阻止对 611/TCP 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/188","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-051.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9908-102","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19421","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0696.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0696","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0696.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0696.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1907.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h3qp-3qwx-3x56/GHSA-h3qp-3qwx-3x56.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/6723edd43ced2a9627d0c0e8bf12d208cfde84d5/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1909.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/2011/gb_cde_rpc_cmsd_service_detect.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0308.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0296","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0296.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0707","title":"HP Visualize Conference FTP 默认配置未授权文件发送漏洞","description":"HP Visualize Conference 的默认 FTP 配置存在授权缺陷，会议参与者可在未经授权的情况下向其他与会者发送文件。攻击者利用该配置漏洞可通过 FTP 传输恶意文件至目标用户系统，结合社会工程学手段诱导用户执行，可能导致任意代码执行或系统被控制。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统上的 Visualize Conference 组件，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，需通过限制 FTP 服务权限或安装厂商补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0707"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:53.430","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9906-099 中提供的 Visualize Conference 安全补丁。同时修改 FTP 配置文件，限制未授权用户的文件传输权限，仅允许已认证的会议参与者进行文件收发。如不需要 FTP 功能，建议直接禁用 Visualize Conference 内置的 FTP 服务，并在防火墙上限制相关端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-050.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/493","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9906-099"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0296.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0254","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0690","title":"HP CDE 将当前目录加入 root 的 PATH 环境变量导致权限提升漏洞","description":"HP CDE（Common Desktop Environment）在设置 root 用户环境变量 PATH 时错误地将当前目录 \".\" 包含在内，导致本地攻击者可在任意目录中放置与系统命令同名的恶意程序，当 root 用户通过 su 或登录进入该目录并执行未指定路径的命令时，恶意程序将以 root 权限自动执行，实现本地提权。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统中运行 CDE 的版本，需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0690"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.300","remediation":"编辑 root 用户的 .profile、.login 或 CDE 系统级配置文件 /etc/dt/config/Xsession.d/ 下的相关脚本，移除 PATH 中的当前目录（即删除 \".\" 或空路径项），确保 PATH 仅包含绝对路径的系统目录（如 /usr/bin:/usr/sbin）。同时建议修改 CDE 启动脚本中 PATH 的拼接方式，使用完整路径调用命令，消除当前目录隐式搜索带来的提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-053.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-100","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0690","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0690.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-427.txt","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/CWE-Expert/blob/f634e911e6c24a1ad8b9619383e2ab3eb2d9ebd4/CWE_corpus/markdown/4_cwe_trimmed_top25.md.txt","https://github.com/ws-researcher/CAEA/blob/098ddb07c83845feda3d1b1d56ef634927954af4/KGA/dataSet/ICNS/entN_ids_1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0248","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0688","title":"HP 软件分发器 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统的软件分发器（Software Distributor，简称 SD）在 10.x 与 11.x 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于 SD 组件在处理特定输入时未对数据长度做充分边界校验，导致攻击者可控的过长数据写入固定大小的缓冲区，进而可覆盖相邻内存并可能实现任意代码执行。影响范围为运行 HPUX 10.x 和 11.x 且启用 SD 服务的系统。攻击条件为攻击者需能够向目标系统的 SD 服务发送特制请求，通常需要一定的本地或相邻网络访问权限。利用方式为构造恶意输入触发缓冲区溢出，造成服务异常或提升权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0688"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.047","remediation":"立即安装 HP-UX 11.11 或更高版本的 HP Software Distributor 补丁 HPD4365-11，或者应用 HPSBUX9907-101 安全更新。如需继续使用 HPUX 10.x，请应用 HP SD 10.20 补丁套件。立即更新系统，关闭不必要的 SD 服务以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/545","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-101","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0688","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0688.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--9b15c9ce-60ad-4d9f-bb76-76ab2ab118a8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0508","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0508.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0726","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 映像头拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 可执行文件加载器在处理 PE 格式映像头时存在输入验证不足漏洞（CWE-20）。本地攻击者可通过构造包含畸形映像头字段（如数据目录项或节表偏移）的恶意 .exe 文件，诱使用户执行后触发未处理异常，导致系统蓝屏崩溃（BSOD），造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 Workstation/Server 及 Terminal Server Edition，需用户交互触发。微软已在 Service Pack 5 中修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0726"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.700","remediation":"Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持且无安全更新可用，建议升级至 Windows Server 2008 及以上版本。如无法升级，可在组策略中限制用户执行非信任程序，并使用进程审计日志监控异常 PE 加载行为作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ234557","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/499","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-023"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0508.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0004","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0140","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RAS/PPTP 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 3.51 及 NT 4.0 的远程访问服务（RAS）与 PPTP 协议实现中存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制的畸形控制数据包，可导致 RAS/PPTP 服务崩溃或停止响应，造成系统无法正常提供远程访问功能。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响范围涉及企业远程接入环境，可能导致业务中断。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0140"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-06-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:40.957","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 或更高版本以修复 RAS/PPTP 协议处理中的缺陷。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2019/2022），并在防火墙上限制对 PPTP 端口（TCP 1723）的访问以降低暴露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20508","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0140","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0140.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r/GHSA-fg49-hp4g-2h7r.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnt_pptp_dos.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0140.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0004.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0715","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0916","title":"WebTrends 账户口令文件权限许可漏洞","description":"WebTrends 软件在安装目录中以明文文件存储账户名和密码，且该文件未设置充分的访问权限限制，导致本地攻击者可通过读取该文件获取敏感凭据信息。攻击者获得凭据后可进一步利用其他服务或系统资源，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响 WebTrends 多个版本，利用条件为攻击者需具备本地文件系统访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0916"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.420","remediation":"将存储用户名和密码的文件（如 web.ini、wtlogin.txt）的 NTFS 权限设置为仅 SYSTEM 和管理员可读取，移除 Everyone 和 Users 组的访问权限；升级 WebTrends 到最新受支持版本；启用 Windows 集成身份验证或加密存储方式替代明文密码文件；定期审计关键文件的 ACL 配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0916"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0715.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0735","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0735.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0938","title":"MBone SDR 会话目录工具远程命令执行漏洞","description":"MBone SDR（会话目录）软件包在处理会话启动协议（SIP）消息时，未对用户输入的 shell 元字符进行过滤，导致存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可向运行 SDR 服务的目标主机发送包含恶意 shell 元字符的特制 SIP 消息，从而以服务进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响多个 SDR 软件版本，攻击复杂度低，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0938"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.043","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 MBone SDR Package，该软件自 1999 年后无任何安全更新。建议迁移至现代会话目录工具（如基于 Web 的会议调度系统）替代。若必须继续使用旧版 SDR，应在应用层严格过滤 SIP 消息中的 `;&|`$()` 等 shell 元字符，同时在网络防火墙层面限制仅允许可信来源 IP 访问 SDR 服务端口（UDP 9875），以降低远程利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0938"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0735.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0346","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0346.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0733","title":"VMware 1.0.1 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"VMware 1.0.1 for Linux 中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序未对 HOME 环境变量的长度进行有效限制，本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 HOME 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，导致权限提升或任意代码执行。攻击者需拥有目标系统的本地访问权限方可利用此漏洞，影响 VMware 1.0.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0733"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.623","remediation":"立即升级 VMware 至 1.1 或更高版本，该版本已修复 HOME 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于 VMware 1.x 系列已停止维护，建议迁移至当前受支持的 VMware Workstation 产品线。若无法升级，应严格限制本地登录用户为可信人员，避免向不可信用户授予 shell 访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/490","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19371"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0346.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0512","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0512.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0778","title":"Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 服务器 4.0.x 及 5.0 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 display 或 query 参数传递超长字符串触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Accelerated-X 4.0.x 及 5.0 系列版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0778"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:02.353","remediation":"该漏洞影响 Xi Graphics Accelerated-X 4.0.x/5.0 及更早版本，厂商已停止维护且无安全补丁。建议立即卸载该软件，迁移至 X.Org Server 等持续维护的开源 X 服务器替代方案。如无法卸载，应限制本地用户登录权限，仅允许受信任用户访问系统控制台，并移除受影响可执行文件的 setuid root 位以降低提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/488","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19370"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0512.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0384","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0384.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0748","title":"Red Hat net-tools 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 系统 net-tools 网络工具包中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可利用精心构造的输入数据触发 ifconfig、route 等命令在解析网络配置信息时的栈溢出，进而导致系统崩溃或提升至 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响早期 Red Hat Linux 发行版，攻击者无需复杂认证条件即可在本地或远程实施利用，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0748"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:58.483","remediation":"建议立即从 Red Hat 官方渠道获取并安装修补后的 net-tools 软件包（RHSA-1999:017-01）。使用命令 `rpm -Uvh net-tools-<修补版本>.rpm` 升级，或通过 Red Hat 提供的更新工具自动安装。如无法升级，可限制本地网络工具执行权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/RHSA1999017_01.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0384.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0873","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1019","title":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Cabletron Spectrum Enterprise Manager 5.0 的 SpectroSERVER 组件在安装时设置了不安全的目录权限，导致本地攻击者可将该目录中的特权可执行文件 processd 替换为特洛伊木马。成功利用该漏洞的攻击者可获得 root 或 Administrator 权限，完全控制目标系统。漏洞利用要求攻击者拥有本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1019"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.087","remediation":"立即修改 Spectrum Enterprise Manager 安装目录（默认路径通常为 /opt/Spectrum 或 C:\\Program Files\\Cabletron\\Spectrum）及其子目录的权限，确保仅 root/Administrator 具有写入权限，普通用户仅保留读取与执行权限；使用 chmod 755 或更严格的权限设置。同时校验 processd 可执行文件的完整性（比对 md5/sha256 哈希值），若发现被替换则从原始安装介质恢复。作为长远方案，建议迁移至仍在维护的网络管理平台。服务器层面配置文件完整性监控（如 Tripwire 或 AIDE），对 processd 等关键二进制文件进行实时变更告警。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398513475&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93024398713491&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/495","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1019","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1019.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836/GHSA-3523-w4qj-m836.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1019.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0873.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0500","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0723","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 CSRSS 工作线程耗尽拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的客户端服务器运行时子系统（CSRSS）存在工作线程耗尽漏洞。当 CSRSS 的所有工作线程均处于等待用户输入状态时，远程攻击者可通过发送大量恶意请求消耗系统可用线程资源，导致 CSRSS 无法处理新的合法请求，从而引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，造成系统服务不可用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0723"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.320","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 针对 Windows NT 4.0 的安全更新 (MS99-032)，此更新限制了 CSRSS 工作线程的数量并解决了线程耗尽问题。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ233323","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-049.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/478","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-021"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0331","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0331.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0731","title":"KDE klock 会话锁定绕过漏洞","description":"KDE klock 屏幕锁定程序存在输入验证缺陷，本地攻击者可通过向锁定界面提交特制的格式错误输入绕过认证机制，从而在无需密码的情况下解锁已锁定的用户会话。该漏洞影响 KDE 1.x 系列版本，攻击者需要具备本地系统访问权限，利用复杂度较低，可导致本地权限提升或未授权访问。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0731"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.367","remediation":"升级 KDE 至 1.1.2 或更高版本，该版本修复了 klock 对输入验证不严的问题。如无法升级，建议禁用屏幕锁定功能或限制本地用户对 klock 二进制文件的执行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/489","https://github.com/KDE/kde1-kdebase/commit/04906bd5de2f220bf100b605dad37b4a1d9a91a6"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0331.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0361","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0361.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0742","title":"Debian Mailman 弱认证权限提升漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 系统中所集成的 Mailman 邮件列表管理软件存在弱身份认证漏洞。由于该软件对用户权限验证机制设计不严谨，攻击者可在无需有效凭证的情况下绕过认证限制，进而获取系统特权或提升自身权限。该漏洞影响 Debian 发行版中的 Mailman 软件包，攻击者利用此漏洞可对邮件服务器造成未授权访问及数据泄露风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0742"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:57.757","remediation":"升级至 mailman 1.0 或更高版本（Debian 下通过 apt-get install mailman 更新），该版本修复了 CGI 管理接口的弱认证机制，强化了密码验证流程。如无法升级，限制 mailman CGI 目录（通常位于 /usr/lib/cgi-bin/mailman/）仅允许可信任 IP 访问，并确保管理员密码强度不低于 16 位混合字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/480"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0361.toml"}]